Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy for Age Calculator App

Effective Date: 18 Jan 2025

SNAGUL.ltd we respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use the Age Calculator app.

Information We Collect
The Age Calculator app does not collect, store, or share any personal data from users. When you input your date of birth and select a specific date for calculation, this data is processed locally on your device. No information is transmitted to our servers or any third parties.

How We Use Your Information
Since the App does not collect any personal data, there is no information usage outside of the local calculations performed on your device.

Third-Party Services
The App does not use third-party services that collect data.

Data Security
We prioritize your privacy and data security. All calculations are performed locally on your device, ensuring no personal data leaves your device.

Children's Privacy
The App is designed for users of all ages. It does not collect any information, including from children under 13.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page. We encourage users to review this page periodically.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
